Text: BlackRock Enhanced Global Dividend Trust (NYSE:BOE) Holdings Decreased by BB&T Securities LLC BB&T Securities LLC lessened its stake in shares of BlackRock Enhanced Global Dividend Trust (NYSE:BOE) by 10.5% during the second quarter, according to the company in its most recent disclosure with the SEC. The fund owned 48,333 shares of the financial services provider's stock after selling 5,662 shares during the quarter. BB&T Securities LLC's holdings in BlackRock Enhanced Global Dividend Trust were worth $518,000 as of its most recent SEC filing.
